ygData.messageBody:
I ran into him again today and let him know that I wasnt the original user.
He was suprise but didnt mind at all. We went to the LOWER level of GUK
today and killed the LORD there and I got Ghoulbane. We are planning to
get together this weekend too. Nice guy! I thought he would be mad but he
didnt mind. Said He didnt use plat much anymore because at 39th level most
of the things he used he got from killing things. I felt a lot better. My
conscience it clear now :-)


Kal-ell

Sandy
